b8524a319a23cB1033fa09" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" targ=
et=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bo=
rder-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: =
solid; background-color: #ccc;"> testifying</a> in Bankman-Fried=E2=80=99s =
criminal trial <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/330=
07895.258422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9yZWFsLWVzdGF0ZS9sdXh1cnktaG9tZXMvcm=
